<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>Default 10% on all automations?</strong> No — trains discount waiting. Proof-first, segment-tiered incentives. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
<p><strong>Collision calendar what?</strong> Shared doc: which layers can offer what depth when — one offer per intent window. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
<p><strong>Full-price loyalist definition?</strong> Typically 3+ orders without code redemption — segment and exclude from promos. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
