<p><strong>Biggest mistake?</strong> Independent 10% defaults in Privy, cart, winback, SMS same week — trains perpetual waiting. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
    </article>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      {toolReviews.map((review) => (
        <ToolReview app={appBySlug(review.slug)!} rank={review.rank} paragraphs={review.paragraphs} />
